---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Government Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">

<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-400">Government Cybersecurity Solutions</h1>

<p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Secure critical infrastructure and public services while meeting regulatory and data sovereignty requirements.</p>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-8 text-center">Key Security Requirements for Government</h2>
<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Critical Infrastructure Protection</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Protect SCADA/ICS and other critical services from nation-state and advanced threats.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: Trellix / Tenable</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Incident Response & Forensics</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Rapid containment, investigation, and recovery for public sector incidents.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: Trellix / ARCON</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Endpoint Detection</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Protect endpoints across government offices and remote workers.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: SentinelOne</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Data Sovereignty & DLP</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Ensure sensitive public-sector data remains within jurisdictional boundaries and is protected.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: Forcepoint</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

</main>

</Layout>
